<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.4">
<l>arumā nilamaṉ ṟaḷappāṉ kuṟaḷā yavuṇaṉ peruvēḷ viyilceṉ ṟiranta</l>
<l>perumāṉ tirunā mampitaṟ ṟinuntam piṟavit tuyarnīṅ kutumeṉ ṉakiṟpīr</l>
<l>karumā kaṭaluḷ kiṭantā ṉuvantu kavainā varavi ṉaṇaippaḷ ḷiyiṉmēl</l>
<l>tirumāl tirumaṅ kaiyoṭā ṭutillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would say, “We are freed of the pain of our own births,</l>
<l rend="indent">babbling the divine names of the lord</l>
<l>Who, going as a dwarf to the demon’s great sacrifice, that day</l>
<l rend="indent">begged to measure the wide, precious earth,”</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai where,</l>
<l rend="indent">on a bed of a forked-tongued serpent,</l>
<l>Tirumāl, he who lies happily in the vast dark sea, dallies with lady Tiru.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
